pegawai terhormat.

272
00:20:51,709 --> 00:20:54,629
Tolong jaga Otonoshin.

273
00:20:56,422 --> 00:21:00,927
Laksamana, anak tuan akan
membawa peranan penting

274
00:21:01,010 --> 00:21:05,056
