277
00:21:09,352 --> 00:21:13,189
Tolong ajar saya dengan baik!

278
00:21:13,690 --> 00:21:15,400
Awak gementar?

279
00:21:18,861 --> 00:21:20,530
Seperkara lagi,

280
00:21:20,613 --> 00:21:24,617
